{
  "3201730": {
    "name": "Flamecraft (龍焰魔法鎮)",
    "steam_appid": 3201730,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/60096edb8b97e9a17d3a2fbaf0b00867.poster.avif?t=1770110343\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/60096edb8b97e9a17d3a2fbaf0b00867.webm?t=1770110343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《龍焰魔法鎮》是一款以回合制为核心的策略桌游，风格轻松可爱，可供 1 至 5 人游玩。玩家将化身守焰人，协助工匠龙与店主用精湛技艺为镇民们带来欢乐。收集并管理资源、使用附魔手段强化商店，施展魔法成为最厉害的守焰人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/4d57c09008188434db71f80fe71c2681.poster.avif?t=1770110343\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/4d57c09008188434db71f80fe71c2681.webm?t=1770110343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏核心在于巧妙地将工匠龙布置在繁华的商业街。这些小龙能帮助玩家从商店收集各类资源，用于施展附魔法术，触发强力技能组合。结识非凡的“奇幻龙”可获得提升声望的特殊能力。你的最终目标是在游戏结束时获得最高的声望点数，赢取“龙焰大师”（Master of Flamecraft）的称号！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/7a0c0d63040780f8b7f7d583bcf1f1d8.avif?t=1770110343\" width=800 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为守焰人，踏入龙族栖居的美妙奇幻世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《龍焰魔法鎮》构筑了一个龙与魔法共存的幻想世界。你将在此处邂逅一群可爱的工匠龙，它们将运用非凡的火焰技艺协助城中的店主完成看似平凡的日常事务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“罪恶糖果店”的甜品即将上架，“龙邻邮政”已准备好向全城投递附魔邮件！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/31d5cf366eee95ab1d9d439dbf9badbe.poster.avif?t=1770110343\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/31d5cf366eee95ab1d9d439dbf9badbe.webm?t=1770110343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验多元游戏模式，单人多人任你玩</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你偏好独自探索、与好友同乐还是全球联机，《龍焰魔法鎮》都将为你提供独特体验。你可选择挑战不同难度的 AI 对手，也能为家人定制轻松惬意的关卡一同享受休闲乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机生成的龙族、店铺与附魔道具相组合，使每局游戏都充满惊喜元素与策略机遇。虽然元素出现的顺序具有随机性，但如何调配资源完全由你掌控，为每次单人或多人游戏带来独特的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/bdc11cd925568bcdecd70e27ed898b17.poster.avif?t=1770110343\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/bdc11cd925568bcdecd70e27ed898b17.webm?t=1770110343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>掌握资源管理的艺术，创造强力组合技提升声望</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要脱颖而出，你需要以精妙策略智胜其他守焰人。通向胜利的途径千变万化，关键在于充分发挥你的技能优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的回合，你将造访城中任意一间店铺，或收集资源，或使用魔法道具为店铺附魔。你可以从“地精杂货店”获取铁材，到“飞龙蛋糕店”采购刚出炉的面包，或前往“龙涎药剂店”调配神秘饮品。收集足够资源后，即可对店铺施法——此举将唤醒店铺中所有的龙，通过各种能力的组合创造出惊艳连击。搭配具备一次性强力技能或终局计分加成的伙伴卡和华丽龙卡，声望点数将迅速增长，助你赢得胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/793b5cae025492db7874fbe5186552e4.poster.avif?t=1770110343\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/793b5cae025492db7874fbe5186552e4.webm?t=1770110343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>邂逅 70 余只有着精美动画的工匠龙，造访 30 家特色店铺，聆听奇妙的幻想乐章</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《龍焰魔法鎮》生动呈现了插画师 Sandara Tang 创造的迷人魔法世界。绘制精美的工匠龙在繁华的 3D 城镇中施展技艺，动画细节丰富的店铺、摊位与实验室构筑出跃动的场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾为《展翅翱翔》《猫与花毯》谱曲的 Paweł Górniak 再度回归，为本作带来美妙的乐章。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您能否在创意无限的工匠龙小伙伴的帮助下，赢得“龙焰大师”的称号？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/6c6c70034f8f4c3fd25e6ea1ca5ee880.poster.avif?t=1770110343\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201730/extras/6c6c70034f8f4c3fd25e6ea1ca5ee880.webm?t=1770110343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
